WEBVTT

00:00:00.765 --> 00:00:02.429
Six months ago,

00:00:02.453 --> 00:00:05.651
I watched with bated breath

00:00:05.675 --> 00:00:09.909
as NASA's InSight lander
descended towards the surface of Mars.

00:00:10.437 --> 00:00:12.095
Two hundred meters,

00:00:12.119 --> 00:00:13.448
80 meters,

00:00:13.472 --> 00:00:17.419
60, 40, 20, 17 meters.

00:00:17.808 --> 00:00:21.262
Receiving confirmation
of successful touchdown

00:00:21.286 --> 00:00:24.427
was one of the most
ecstatic moments of my life.

00:00:25.294 --> 00:00:30.930
And hearing that news was possible
because of two small cube sets